div.data-content:
## 1.3

由题目有

$$m(x)\omega^2 W(x) = EI(x)\frac{\partial^4 W(x)}{\partial x^4}$$

则有

$$
\begin{align*}
m\omega_i^2\int_0^L W_j(x) W_i(x) \, dx &= EI\int_0^L \frac{\partial^4 W_i(x)}{\partial x^4} W_j(x) \, dx \\
&= \left. EI\frac{\partial^3 W_i(x)}{\partial x^3} W_j(x) \right|_0^L - EI\int_0^L \frac{\partial^3 W_i(x)}{\partial x^3} \frac{\partial W_j(x)}{\partial x} \, dx \\
&= -EI\int_0^L \frac{\partial^3 W_i(x)}{\partial x^3} \frac{\partial W_j(x)}{\partial x} \, dx \\
&= -\left. EI\frac{\partial^2 W_i(x)}{\partial x^2} \frac{\partial W_j(x)}{\partial x} \right|_0^L + EI\int_0^L \frac{\partial^2 W_i(x)}{\partial x^2} \frac{\partial^2 W_j(x)}{\partial x^2} \, dx \\
&= EI\int_0^L \frac{\partial^2 W_i(x)}{\partial x^2} \frac{\partial^2 W_j(x)}{\partial x^2} \, dx
\end{align*}
$$

同理，

$$
m\omega_j^2\int_0^L Y_i(x) Y_j(x) \, dx = EI\int_0^L \frac{\partial^2 Y_j(x)}{\partial x^2} \frac{\partial^2 Y_i(x)}{\partial x^2} \, dx
$$

所以

$$
\left( \omega_i^2 - \omega_j^2 \right) \int_0^L Y_i(x) m Y_j(x) \, dx = 0
$$

因为$\omega _i^2 \ne \omega _j^2$,所以

$$
\left( \omega_i^2 - \omega_j^2 \right) \int_0^L Y_i(x) m Y_j(x) \, dx = 0
$$

所以

$$\int_0^L Y_i(x) m Y_j(x) \, dx = 0$$

\int_0^L Y_i(x) m Y_j(x) \, dx &= m\int_0^L \left( \sin(\alpha_2 x) + \frac{\sin(\alpha_2 L)}{\sinh(\alpha_2 L)}\sinh(\alpha_2 x) \right) \\
&\quad \left( \sin(\alpha_3 x) + \frac{\sin(\alpha_3 L)}{\sinh(\alpha_3 L)}\sinh(\alpha_3 x) \right) \, dx \\
&= 0, \quad i,j = 1,2,3, \quad i \ne j
\end{align*}
$$
